{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-doc-page-template-tsx","path":"/docs/hotchocolate/v10/examples","result":{"data":{"file":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"fields":{"slug":"/hotchocolate/v10/examples/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Star Wars"},"html":"<p>We have created the Star Wars sample in different versions in order to show different ways to build your GraphQL server off.</p>\n<h1 id=\"pure-code-first\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#pure-code-first\" aria-label=\"pure code first permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Pure Code-First</h1>\n<p>Pure Code-First is our newest variant to build GraphQL by just using clean C#. You really do not need to deal with schema types directly and you still get all the power that you would have with schema types. You can split types use field middleware and all of this without any clutter.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"63854116734244995000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied code example\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`public class Query\n{\n    /// <summary>\n    /// Gets all character.\n    /// </summary>\n    /// <param name=&quot;repository&quot;></param>\n    /// <returns>The character.</returns>\n    [UsePaging]\n    [UseFiltering]\n    [UseSorting]\n    public IEnumerable<ICharacter> GetCharacters(\n        [Service]ICharacterRepository repository) =>\n        repository.GetCharacters();\n}`, `63854116734244995000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"csharp\"><pre class=\"language-csharp\"><code class=\"language-csharp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Query</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/// &lt;summary></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/// Gets all character.</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/// &lt;/summary></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/// &lt;param name=\"repository\">&lt;/param></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/// &lt;returns>The character.&lt;/returns></span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>UsePaging<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token attribute\"><span class=\"token class-name\">UseFiltering</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token attribute\"><span class=\"token class-name\">UseSorting</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token return-type class-name\">IEnumerable<span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ICharacter<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> <span class=\"token function\">GetCharacters</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token attribute\"><span class=\"token class-name\">Service</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token class-name\">ICharacterRepository</span> repository<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span>\n        repository<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">GetCharacters</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/ChilliCream/hotchocolate-examples/tree/master/misc/PureCodeFirst\">Star Wars - Pure Code-First</a></p>\n<p>We have also created a dotnet CLI template for the pure Code-First Star Wars example. You can follow the example and get an impression how you could implement such a schema with our API.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"11104870376100907000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied code example\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`dotnet new -i HotChocolate.Templates.StarWars`, `11104870376100907000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">dotnet new -i HotChocolate.Templates.StarWars</code></pre></div>\n<p>After you have installed this template you can just fire up the following command in order to get the example up and running:</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"84532289555787270000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied code example\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`mkdir starwars\ncd starwars\ndotnet new starwars\ndotnet run --project StarWars/StarWars.csproj -c release`, `84532289555787270000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> starwars\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> starwars\ndotnet new starwars\ndotnet run --project StarWars/StarWars.csproj -c release</code></pre></div>\n<p>The service should start-up and run on the port 5000. In order to test your server and send queries head over to our playground endpoint: <code class=\"language-text\">http://127.0.0.1:5000/graphql/playground</code></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Note: The port may vary depending on if you start this project from the console with <code class=\"language-text\">dotnet run</code> or from Visual Studio.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Try a query like the following to get started:</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"8431802020478530000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied code example\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`{\n  character(ids: 1000) {\n    name\n    appearsIn\n    friends {\n      nodes {\n        name\n        appearsIn\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}`, `8431802020478530000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"graphql\"><pre class=\"language-graphql\"><code class=\"language-graphql\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  character<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token attr-name\">ids</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    name\n    appearsIn\n    friends <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      nodes <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        name\n        appearsIn\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>The template source code is located <a href=\"https://github.com/ChilliCream/hotchocolate/tree/master/examples\">here</a>.</p>\n<h1 id=\"code-first\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#code-first\" aria-label=\"code first permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Code-First</h1>\n<p>Code-First or Code-First with schema types lets you use our fluent type API to describe your schema types. The resolver code and the actual types are disjunct you explicitly can express your schema types without even needing a C# backing type.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"40503307164647670000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied code example\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`public class QueryType : ObjectType<Query>\n{\n   protected override Configure(IObjectTypeDescriptor<Query> descriptor)\n   {\n      descriptor.Field(t => t.GetCharacters(default))\n         .UsePaging<NonNullType<CharacterType>>()\n         .UseFiltering()\n         .UseSorting();\n   }\n}\n\npublic class Query\n{\n    /// <summary>\n    /// Gets all character.\n    /// </summary>\n    /// <param name=&quot;repository&quot;></param>\n    /// <returns>The character.</returns>\n    public IEnumerable<ICharacter> GetCharacters(\n        [Service]ICharacterRepository repository) =>\n        repository.GetCharacters();\n}`, `40503307164647670000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"csharp\"><pre class=\"language-csharp\"><code class=\"language-csharp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">QueryType</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token type-list\"><span class=\"token class-name\">ObjectType<span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Query<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">override</span> <span class=\"token function\">Configure</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">IObjectTypeDescriptor<span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Query<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> descriptor<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      descriptor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">Field</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>t <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> t<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">GetCharacters</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">default</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n         <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token generic-method\"><span class=\"token function\">UsePaging</span><span class=\"token generic class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>NonNullType<span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>CharacterType<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n         <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">UseFiltering</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n         <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">UseSorting</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Query</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/// &lt;summary></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/// Gets all character.</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/// &lt;/summary></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/// &lt;param name=\"repository\">&lt;/param></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/// &lt;returns>The character.&lt;/returns></span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token return-type class-name\">IEnumerable<span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ICharacter<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> <span class=\"token function\">GetCharacters</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token attribute\"><span class=\"token class-name\">Service</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token class-name\">ICharacterRepository</span> repository<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span>\n        repository<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">GetCharacters</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/ChilliCream/hotchocolate-examples/tree/master/misc/CodeFirst\">Star Wars - Code-First</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"schema-first\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#schema-first\" aria-label=\"schema first permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Schema-First</h1>\n<p>We are currently working on a schema-first example. Example Coming Soon :)</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/hotchocolate/v10/examples/#pure-code-first\">Pure Code-First</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/hotchocolate/v10/examples/#code-first\">Code-First</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/hotchocolate/v10/examples/#schema-first\">Schema-First</a></li>\n</ul>"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://chillicream.com","repositoryUrl":"https://github.com/ChilliCream/hotchocolate","tools":{"slack":"https://join.slack.com/t/hotchocolategraphql/shared_invite/enQtNTA4NjA0ODYwOTQ0LTViMzA2MTM4OWYwYjIxYzViYmM0YmZhYjdiNzBjOTg2ZmU1YmMwNDZiYjUyZWZlMzNiMTk1OWUxNWZhMzQwY2Q"}}},"config":{"products":[{"path":"hotchocolate","title":"Hot Chocolate","description":"Build your own thin GraphQL API layer on top of any resource.","versions":[{"path":"v10","title":"v10 (stable)","items":[{"path":"index","title":"Introduction","items":null},{"path":"code-first","title":"Code-First","items":null}